specifications.rawSpecificationsHTML: NAZARÉ DAYBED - L shape, designed in 2024. The Nazaré Daybed is crafted from solid walnut and has two removable cushions. The legs have a hand-carved detailed wave texture giving the piece it's name. Available in customer’s own material. Please inquire to view other wood and fabric options. Production lead time: 8-12 weeks
